I think we can default this in buildah pkg if session is `rootless` and we are falling back to native overlay. @giuseppe WDYT ?

@leahneukirchen you can try with vendoring in following commit https://github.com/flouthoc/buildah/commit/f75d59698138d6d904d9ea516fd188a2467ce649 to podman . I'll open a PR once @giuseppe confirms

```diff
index 84b0e12b..262df7c3 100644
--- a/pkg/overlay/overlay.go
+++ b/pkg/overlay/overlay.go
@@ -142,6 +142,8 @@ func mountHelper(contentDir, source, dest string, _, _ int, graphOptions []strin
                        mount.Type = "bind"
                        mount.Options = []string{"bind", "slave"}
                        return mount, nil
+               } else {
+                       overlayOptions = fmt.Sprintf("%s,userxattr", overlayOptions)
                }
                /* If a mount_program is not specified, fallback to try mount native overlay.  */
        }
```
